       <div>
        <h1 class="h1">
         Welcome
        </h1>
        <div class="rich-text">
         <p>
          Berkeley Loyal members provide critical, ongoing support that helps transform students’ lives and shapes our world for the better. When you
          <a href="https://loyal.berkeley.edu/faq/#q1">
           make gifts in each of the three most recent fiscal years (July 1–June 30)
          </a>
          or you
          <a href="https://loyal.berkeley.edu/faq/#q4">
           make a gift while you are a senior
          </a>
          , you achieve the distinction of Berkeley Loyal.
          <a href="https://loyal.berkeley.edu/faq/#q6">
           You are recognized
          </a>
          for the total number of years in which you’ve made gifts to Cal.
         </p>
         <p>
          More than 26,000 donor households currently qualify as Berkeley Loyal, 61 of which have given consistently for 50 years (or more)!
         </p>
         <p>
          Year in and year out, loyal supporters play a starring role in helping our students and faculty achieve their dreams and change the world.
         </p>
        </div>
        <p class="callout">
         Fiat Lux!
        </p>
       </div>
